The SSG08 bolt-action is a low-damage but very cost-effective sniper rifle, making it a smart choice for early-round long-range marksmanship. It has been hand painted to resemble a death's-head hawkmoth. Quid pro quo

Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a production line yellow color scheme. This bone crusher is a devastator
This item commemorates ESL One Cologne 2016 CS:GO Championship.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This foil sticker was autographed by professional player Mikhail Stoliarov playing for Gambit Gaming at Cologne 2016.

50% of the proceeds from the sale of this sticker support the included players and organizations.

A less expensive option among the terrorist-exclusive assault rifles, the Galil AR is a serviceable weapon in medium to long-range combat. It has been painted using a Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic. By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late
This item commemorates ESL One Cologne 2015 CS:GO Championship.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This foil sticker was autographed by professional player Kenny Schrub playing for Team EnVyUs at ESL One Cologne 2015.

50% of the proceeds from the sale of this sticker support the included players and organizations.

The classic Sawed-Off deals very heavy close-range damage, but with its low accuracy, high spread and slow rate of fire, you'd better kill what you hit. Its stock has been wrapped in green leather. Mimosa not included
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. It has been painted with the image of a skull and roots using high-durability enamel paints. There are some roots you don't want to take hold

An ideal pistol for the Terrorist on the move, the Tec-9 is lethal in close quarters and features a high magazine capacity. It has been painted with a hydrographic in a geometric motif. You're too trusting Valeria... it will get you killed - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. It has been painstakingly engraved. Naomi understands that one day she will die for Valeria

Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. It has been custom painted using a combination of hydrographics and careful stenciling and detailed with heat-transfer decals. Tread softly Naomi...people in your line of work aren't known for their longevity - The Shield and The Serpent Part 2
This item commemorates DreamHack Cluj-Napoca 2015 CS:GO Championship.

The pricy G3SG1 lowers movement speed considerably but compensates with a higher rate of fire than other sniper rifles. Originally green, parts of the weapon have been replaced with street signs and a tomato can. Why run?

The XM1014 is a powerful fully automatic shotgun that justifies its heftier price tag with the ability to paint a room with lead fast. Its stock and grip have been wrapped in red leather. Pack your baags. Let's go kill that sonofabitch... - The Oni and The Valkyrie Part 2

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. It has been custom painted with the image of a flying bullet, then weathered with sandpaper.

descriptions.value: This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.
This item tracks Official Competitive MVPs.

This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP.

The Music Kit replaces the following music:
- Main Menu
- Round Start and End
- Map Objective
- Ten Second Warning
- Death Camera
Composer Daniel Sadowski raises the bar with aggressive electronic beats, creative sound fx and an exhilerating, driving, futuristic vibe. "Warning: Will cause a rise in adrenaline!"
